quran[19{c,v,t}:
19,77,phir to ne dekha uss shakhs ko jo hamari ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar karta hai aur kehta hai ke mein to maal aur aulaad se nawaza hi jata rahon ga ?
19,78,kya usay ghaib ka pata chal gaya hai ya is ne Rehman se koi ehad le rakha hai ?
19,79,"hargiz nahi, jo kuch yeh bikta hai usay hum likh len ge aur is ke liye saza mein aur ziyada izafah karen ge"
19,80,jis sir o samaan aur lao lashkar ka yeh zikar kar raha hai woh sab hamaray paas reh jaye ga aur yeh akela hamaray samnay haazir hoga
19,81,inn logon ne Allah ko chore kar apne kuch khuda bana rakhay hain taakay woh inn ke pshtiban hon
19,82,koi pshtiban nah hoga woh sab un ki ibadat ka inkaar karen ge aur ultay inn ke mukhalif ban jayen ge
19,83,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke hum ne inn munkareen haq par shyatin chore rakhay hain jo aِnhin khob khob ( Mukhalfat haq par ) aksa rahay hain ?
19,84,"acha, to ab inn par nuzool azaab ke liye betaab nah ho hum inn ke din gun rahay hain"
19,85,woh din anay wala hai jab mut-taqi logon ko hum mehmanon ki terhan Rehman ke huzoor paish karen ge
19,86,aur mujrimon ko pyase janwaron ki terhan jahannum ki taraf haank le jayen ge
19,87,uss waqt log koi sifarish laane par Qadir nah hon ge bajuz uss ke jis ne Rehman ke huzoor se parwana haasil kar liya ho
19,88,woh kehte hain ke Rehman ne kisi ko beta banaya hai
19,89,sakht behooda baat hai jo tum log ghurr laaye ho
19,90,"qareeb hai ke aasman phatt parrin, zameen shaqq ho jaye aur pahar gir jayen"
19,91,is baat par ke logon ne Rehman ke liye aulaad honay ka daawa kya !
19,92,Rehman ki yeh shaan nahi hai ke woh kisi ko beta banaye
19,93,zameen aur aasman ke andar jo bhi hain sab is ke huzoor bundon ki hesiyat se paish honay walay hain
19,94,sab par woh muheet hai aur is ne unn ko shumaar kar rakha hai
19,95,sab qayamat ke roz fardan fardan is ke samnay haazir hon ge
